{
  "stem": "16.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 16.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they wound up among the first rows-- first 5 or 10 rows, and so on.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I did the same thing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Pretty soon, I wind up pretty close to the last row again.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What happened, the Germans were having fun.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And every now and then, they were shooting down a guy that seemed very tired and all that.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But also, it happened that if you sat down for a moment because you couldn't take it, they shot you right there.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The snow was red with blood all the time, wherever you were walking.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And this friend of mine, who-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] his father was, was the manager of a-- of the Jewish bank in Munkacs.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And he-- the two of us were walking always together.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The two of us did a lot of things together only because-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] that's another story.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I'll have to come back to that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Anyway, he said to me, at, at one point, he says-- [NON-ENGLISH], I'm gonna sit--",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So this friend of mine, he says to me, I can't take it anymore.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'm going to sit down.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I said, no, you're not going to sit down because they're going to shoot you right there.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But I can't walk anymore.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I says, what am I gonna-- and I started yelling at him.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What am I going to tell your mother, you know, that I just let you die like that?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And you sat down, and they shot you?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You are not sitting down!",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I literally practically dragged him along-- I mean, talked with him.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he finally made it to the barn that night, you know, and so on.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so nothing happened.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so he died two years ago in, in Tel Aviv.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
